ching\n79\t   - Shows 404 message if profile is null and not loading\n80\t   - Shows error message if fetch fails\n81\t   - Renders identity cluster section: user IDs and device IDs as MUI `Chip` components\n82\t   - Renders first seen / last seen as formatted dates\n83\t   - Renders `UserTimeline` with the profile's events\n84\t   - `data-testid=\"user-profile\"` on the container\n85\t   - `data-testid=\"identity-cluster\"` on the cluster section\n86\t\n87\t## Sprint contract\n88\t\n89\t- [ ] Test suite → `pnpm test` exits 0 with 0 failures\n90\t- [ ] Linter → `pnpm lint` exits 0\n91\t- [ ] Type check → `pnpm typecheck` exits 0\n92\t- [ ] Build → `pnpm build` exits 0\n93\t- [ ] File `src/components/users/useUserProfile.ts` exists and exports `useUserProfile`\n94\t- [ ] File `src/components/users/__tests__/useUserProfile.test.ts` exists\n95\t- [ ] File `src/components/UserTimeline.tsx` exists and exports `UserTimeline`\n96\t- [ ] File `src/app/users/[id]/page.tsx` exists and contains `\"use client\"`\n97\t- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/users/test` contains `data-testid=\"user-profile\"`\n98\t- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/users/test` contains `data-testid=\"identity-cluster\"`\n99\t- [ ] HTTP check: GET `http://localhost:3000/users/test` contains `data-testid=\"user-timeline\"`\n100\t\n101\t## Test plan\n102\t\n103\t- **Test file**: `src/components/users/__tests__/useUserProfile.test.ts`\n104\t- **Module under test**: `useUserProfile` from `@/components/users/useUserProfile`\n105\t- **Cases to cover**:\n106\t  - Fetches profile from `/api/users/{id}` on mount\n107\t  - Sets `loading` to `true` during fetch, `false` after completion\n108\t  - Populates `profile` with API response data on success\n109\t  - Sets `error` when API returns 404\n110\t  - Sets `error` when fetch fails (network error)\n111\t  - Re-fetches when `resolved_id` parameter changes\n112\t  - URL-encodes the resolved_id (e.g. `user@example.com` → `user%40example.com`)\n11